txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Large wings from the hendrevail found throughout the northern North Downs. Deliver the items to Birgir Listmaster at Othrikar.
'Let me see here...yes, a task to collect large wings. The Dourhands needed this lesson. We are grateful.'

'I do have notation of a task to collect large wings from hendrevail. These birds are not all bad, but the ones around here are trained by the Dourhands, a rotten lot of dwarves that we Longbeards stand against.'
Birgir Listmaker, one of the miners at Othrikar in the northern reaches of the North Downs, awaits the delivery of large wings.
Deliver the large wings to Birgir Listmaker at Othrikar
